div.div:
- Query Google Drive for latest .txt file
- If file is older than 15 min → set experimentRunning = false
Else:
- Fetch and reverse file contents
- Parse log lines to update pressure, temperature, flags
- Set experimentRunning = true, shouldReload = true
- Called every 60 sec
